node.text:
You should definitely check out the Group Buy feature on Bluewill (@bluewill_official) at https://in.bluewill.com/t/V to get cheaper prices on the products you want!

When purchasing a product on Bluewill, you can select a group size of 2 or 5. You are required to pre-pay the Group Buy price, and then invite your friends to join your group. Once the group members are all registered, all the members will get the product at a cheaper price.

If any members fail to register within 24 hours, all the funds will be refunded automatically. [Ad]
